                "description": {
                    "value": "<b>Requirements</b> The monsterâ€™s last action was a success with a Strike that lists Grab in its damage entry, or it has a creature grabbed using this action. <b>Effect</b> The monster automatically Grabs the target until the end of the monsterâ€™s next turn. The creature is grabbed by whichever body part the monster attacked with, and that body part canâ€™t be used to Strike creatures until the grab is ended.<br><br> Using Grab extends the duration of the monsterâ€™s Grab until the end of its next turn for all creatures grabbed by it. A grabbed creature can use the @Compendium[pf2e.actionspf2e.Escape] action to get out of the grab, and the Grab ends for a grabbed creatures if the monster moves away from it.",
